data.description: Won't Last Long! Enjoy this beautiful custom home that offers a beautiful view of the conservation double lot  off the large pool lanai! This home boasts a quite setting custom built 4 br 3 bath 3 cg split FP just 3,044 sq ft of  heated space. This homes entryway and living area features with 12 ft ceilings & tiled flooring. This home has a  large kitchen with double-wall convection oven, featuring Corian countertops, 42'' maple cabinets, island &  prep-sink. The large family room with fireplace overlooks the conservation area and the living room has glass  slider pocket doors so you can open to the outdoors and enjoy the oversized paved lanai, sparkling pool &  private spa, heated for year-round entertaining, 40 ft swim lane, outdoor shower. This home has to be seen to  be appreciated, as it is meticulously maintained. Scheduled your showing today! Buyers to verify room  dimensions.
